Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样做有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 对手可是像刺猬一般的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管什么刺不刺猬的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能进入里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来 那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜丽亚 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 那个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太的乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用骷髅三号机收集的数据进行了模拟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大航速的话 我方占优
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 米娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船各部无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是改装后的第一次 但我认为可行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 莫尼卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在炮击模式上编排了回避程序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领航就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 请等等 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒然挺进的话太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说驾驶员在敌舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 如果我们就此逃走 Dulfim的船员将全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕Galaxy的安危也会变得不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所传达的总统指示是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们尚有完成该指示的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自相残杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quarter向所有出击部队传令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将进入与Vajra航空母舰的近距离格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗战!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于登场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位请全力保护Dulfim
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的猎物就交给我这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 变形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将开始变形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各船员 开始强攻型配置切换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主反应炉 输出功率上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分形模型系统(Fractale Module System)激活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我还没有完全赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比 Quarter为何只有400米级别\N却被冠以Macross之称
